Usage: moveSdpObject [-help] <moveObject {objName(s)}> {-before <refObject> | -after <refObject>}

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<moveObject {objName(s)}>     # Name of objects to be moved (string, required)
-after <refObject>            # move objects after reference object
                              # (string, required)
-before <refObject>           # move objects before reference object
                              # (string, required)